posts.description: Thank you so much for all the kind words on Monday's post and kitchen reveal. We have been having such an amazing time remodeling this home of ours and sharing it with you guys! We added a few more sources with links to the blog post for some of the decor pieces, but if you guys are curious about anything let us know! ❤️ http://liketk.it/2ra21 #liketkit @liketoknow.it #newdarlingsHOME

Today on the blog (link in profile), we are revealing our newly remodeled kitchen. It has quickly become our favorite room in the house and we are so excited to share ALL of the details with you guys. Head on over and check it out 👀 , let us know what you think, and see some before + afters 🙌🏼😊 #newdarlingsHOME http://liketk.it/2r8tJ #liketkit @liketoknow.it

Shooting a fun project today for the blog, but this morning looked a lot like this. 👌🏼 We dug out a couple of my great uncle's old art books, brewed a few cups of espresso, and got in some good puppies cuddles. 🐶❤️ What's everyone up to? http://liketk.it/2r7SU #liketkit @liketoknow.it
Happy Earth Day from our plant babies to yours. 🌿💦 🌏 ☀️ http://liketk.it/2r7kY #liketkit @liketoknow.it #everdaymadewell #schoolhouseliving #newdarlingsHOME

Sunshine and bike rides are good for the soul! 🙌🏼☀️🚲 Can't wait to get a little basket for Henry so he can ride around with us too! ☺️💕 http://liketk.it/2r5YP #liketkit @liketoknow.it #everydaymadewell

We are so honored to be featured on @schoolhouse's blog today, sharing a peek into our little 1930s Tudor. Head to their page to see more photos and a special Q&A about our home and move to Arizona. Their ode to purposeful living, and focus on wanting better not more, really resonates with us. ❤️ We also shared some of our #schoolhouseelectric favorites on our blog today as well. So if you're looking for some design inspiration, check it out. 😊👉🏼Link in profile. #schoolhouseliving #newdarlingsHOME
Sunny days when you don't feel like doing your hair and need some pesto mac n cheese. 👌🏼😜 http://liketk.it/2r4zp #liketkit @liketoknow.it

A glimpse at this morning's weekly food prep. (Full blog post on the space coming next week!) We've really been enjoying trying new recipes and just spending some quality time together over meals. Eating Purely and The Weekend Cook are quickly becoming two of our new favorite cookbooks for recipe inspiration. So good!👌🏼😋 Please share some of your favorites with us! 🍋🥒🌶🌽🥕 We found ourselves getting a little sentimental over the weekend about how connected we already feel to this home and dreaming of the memories yet to be made here. Guess a warm belly can do that to ya! 😂😜 #newdarlingsHOME

We've been hanging around this yard as much as we can lately. We know those triple digit temps will be here before we know it and we are getting our time in! On Monday we are starting the work on our back patio area. So much progress over here lately and as exciting as it is, we are just looking forward to getting "back to normal". Can't believe we've been in this house for five months already! 😱❤️ #newdarlingsHOME

Found this vintage oil painting last week at an antique shop in town and knew we had to bring it home with us. Loving the warm tone it adds to the space. Also after having no idea what to do with this little corner by our entryway, we finally decided to add our guitars along side the record player. It's been so nice having them out in the main room of our house. Evening tunes every night please! ✨ 💃🏻👌🏼 http://liketk.it/2r1pG @liketoknow.it #liketkit @liketoknow.it.home #LTKHome #newdarlingsHOME
